column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: TRIDENT SPLASH GUM PEPPERMINT 58.5 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 00000050105052
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

INGREDIENTS: Sweeteners (maltitol, sorbitol, maltitol syrup, sorbitol syrup, aspartame, acesulfame K), gum base, flavourings, humectant (glycerol), gelatine (bovine), colours (E171, E133), emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), glazing agent (carnauba wax), thickener (E466).  Excessive consumption may produce laxative effects. Contains a source of phenylalanine.. Date available: 02/23/2018 Date last updated by company: 02/23/2018
